                            <apex:outputPanel rendered="{!OR(examAdminType == 'MAY',examAdminType == 'JUL',examAdminType == 'APR')}"> January 31, 2022 </apex:outputPanel>
                            <apex:outputPanel rendered="{!OR(examAdminType == 'NOV',examAdminType == 'DEC',examAdminType == 'AUG')}"> July 31, 2022 </apex:outputPanel>
                        deadline. If your payment is received after the deadline, you will be charged the Standard Rate; in which case you will be required to make an additional payment.
                    </apex:outputPanel>
                    
                    <apex:outputPanel layout="block" rendered="{!examRegistrationType == 'standard'}">
                        <b> <span class="bold-text">Payment:</span></b> In order for your registration to be considered complete based on the Standard Registration rate, your payment must be received by the 
                            <apex:outputPanel rendered="{!OR(examAdminType == 'MAY',examAdminType == 'JUL',examAdminType == 'APR')}"> March 31, 2022 </apex:outputPanel>
                            <apex:outputPanel rendered="{!OR(examAdminType == 'NOV',examAdminType == 'DEC')}"> September 30, 2022 </apex:outputPanel>
                        deadline. If your payment is received after the deadline, your registration will be cancelled; as registration is closed.
                    </apex:outputPanel>
