                        <br/>Please reference your GARP ID and Invoice Number when sending your payment.
                        <br/>
                        <p>
                            Make your check payable to: <b> <span class="bold-text">Global Association of Risk Professionals, Inc.</span></b>
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Mail your check to: <b> <span class="bold-text">Attn: Accounting, 111 Town Square Place, 14th floor, Jersey City, NJ 07310 USA</span></b>                
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            GARP accepts checks drawn on US banks, or foreign checks drawn on a US Intermediate Bank account.            
                        </p>
                    </p>
                    
                </apex:outputPanel>
                
                <apex:outputPanel layout="block" rendered="{!Membership}">
                    <p>
                        <b> <span class="bold-text">Membership:</span></b> As a convenience to you, GARP can automatically renew this membership every year from your initial sign-up-date. If you would like to opt-out of this service, please contact us directly at memberservices@garp.com. 
                    </p>
                </apex:outputPanel>
                
                <p><b> <span class="bold-text">FRM Program Enrollment:</span></b> Once you have passed the FRM Exam Part I, the enrollment fee is good for 4 years. If you still have not passed FRM Exam Part II by December 31 of the 4th year of passing the FRM Part I, you will need to re-enroll in the program as a new candidate and take the FRM Exam Part I again.</p>
                
                <p><b> <span class="bold-text">Refunds:</span></b> There are no refunds given under any circumstances. Nor can candidates transfer their registration to another.
                </p>
                
            </apex:outputPanel>
            
            <apex:outputPanel layout="block" rendered="{!FRM && CreditByFax}">
                
                <p><b> <span class="bold-text">Important Information:</span></b></p>
                
                <apex:outputPanel layout="block" rendered="{!status=='Paid'}">
                    <p><b> <span class="bold-text">Payment:</span></b> Thank you for your order.</p>
                </apex:outputPanel>
                
                <apex:outputPanel layout="block" rendered="{!status!='Paid'}">
                    
                    <p><b> <span class="bold-text">Fax Payment Instructions:</span></b>
                        <br/>
                        <br/>Complete the information below, sign and fax it back to us at +1.201.222.5022.
                        
