                        <br/>
                        <br/>Card Number: _______________________________________
                        <br/>
                        <br/>CVV Code: ______ Expiration Date: _____________
                        <br/>
                        <br/>Signature of Approval: _____________________________________
                        <br/>
                        <br/>Print your name as it appears on your credit card: _____________________________________
                    </p>
                    
                    <apex:outputPanel layout="block" rendered="{!examRegistrationType == 'early'}">
                        <p>
                            For your registration to be considered complete and based on the *Early Registration rate, your payment must be received by the 
                            <apex:outputPanel rendered="{!OR(examAdminType == 'MAY',examAdminType == 'JUL',examAdminType == 'APR')}"> January 31, 2022 </apex:outputPanel>
                            <apex:outputPanel rendered="{!OR(examAdminType == 'NOV',examAdminType == 'DEC',examAdminType == 'AUG')}"> July 31, 2022 </apex:outputPanel>
                            deadline. If your payment is received after the deadline, you will be charged the rate effective when your payment is received, in which case you will be required to make an additional payment.           
                        </p>  
                    </apex:outputPanel>
                    
                    <apex:outputPanel layout="block" rendered="{!examRegistrationType == 'standard'}">
                        <p>
                            For your registration to be considered complete and based on the *Standard Registration rate, your payment must be received by the 
                            <apex:outputPanel rendered="{!OR(examAdminType == 'MAY',examAdminType == 'JUL',examAdminType == 'APR')}"> March 31, 2022 </apex:outputPanel>
                            <apex:outputPanel rendered="{!OR(examAdminType == 'NOV',examAdminType == 'DEC')}"> September 30, 2022 </apex:outputPanel>
                            deadline. If your payment is received after the deadline, your registration will be cancelled; as registration is closed.
                        </p>  
                    </apex:outputPanel>
                                        
                </apex:outputPanel>
                
